%% Helpdesk agent orchestration — multi-turn loop on a time axis
%%
%% Reviewer narrative:
%%   "Is this really agentic, or just a chain of LLM calls?"
%%   This diagram shows the supervisor picking next_action, tools returning
%%   observations, pause/resume across SSE, and the HITL gate on file_ticket.
%%
%% Companion diagrams:
%%   - helpdesk_agent_state_v3.mmd      (state machine + 4 terminal outcomes)
%%   - architecture_detailed_v3.mmd     (system context)
%%   - rag_pipeline_v3.mmd              (the path the agent escalates from)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Vue as Vue (AGENT mode)
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>/api/helpdesk/agent/*
    participant Sup as Supervisor LLM<br/>(LangGraph node)
    participant Tools as Agent tools<br/>retry_kb · web_search ·<br/>search_dups · file_ticket
    participant Ext as External<br/>GitHub · Tavily
    participant State as SQLite checkpointer<br/>session_id · 24h TTL
    participant Obs as LangSmith · Prometheus

    Note over User,Vue: Triggered when RAG returns metadata.kb_resolved=false

    User->>Vue: Get help
    Vue->>API: POST /agent/start/stream
    API->>Sup: initial state + question
    Note over Sup: budgets enforced<br/>max steps · per-tool · per-token<br/>HELPDESK_AGENT_KILL_SWITCH

    %% Iteration 1 — supervisor picks a tool, sees observation
    Sup-->>Sup: next_action = retry_kb
    Sup->>Tools: retry_kb(reformulated query)
    Tools->>Ext: provider call via registry
    Ext-->>Tools: documents
    Tools-->>Sup: observation
    Sup-->>Obs: per-node span · tokens · latency

    %% Pause for clarifying question
    Sup-->>Sup: next_action = clarify
    Sup-->>API: AgentTurn(clarify · question · choices)
    API-->>Vue: SSE status events ... AgentTurn
    Vue-->>User: render question + radio chips
    User->>Vue: reply
    Vue->>API: POST /agent/resume/stream
    API->>State: load checkpoint(session_id)
    State-->>Sup: resumed state

    %% Iteration 2 — search for duplicate, branch to linked or write draft
    Sup-->>Sup: next_action = search_dups
    Sup->>Tools: search_dups(text)
    Tools->>Ext: GitHub issue search
    Ext-->>Tools: candidate issues
    alt duplicate match
        Tools-->>Sup: link suggestion
        Sup-->>API: AgentTurn(outcome=linked, url)
        API-->>Obs: helpdesk_agent_outcome_total{linked}
    else no duplicate · draft a ticket
        Sup-->>Sup: next_action = write_draft
        Sup->>Tools: write_draft (specialist LLM)
        Tools-->>Sup: TicketDraft
        Sup-->>API: AgentTurn(draft_ready · draft)
        API-->>Vue: SSE done
        Vue-->>User: review modal (TICKET_REVIEW)

        %% HITL gate — file_ticket reachable only via /agent/confirm
        User->>Vue: Confirm
        Vue->>API: POST /agent/confirm
        Note over API,Tools: HITL gate · redaction applied to draft<br/>and again to outbound issue body
        API->>Tools: file_ticket(redacted draft)
        Tools->>Ext: POST /repos/{demo}/issues
        Ext-->>Tools: issue URL
        Tools-->>API: AgentTurn(outcome=filed, url)
        API-->>Obs: helpdesk_agent_outcome_total{filed}
    end

    Note over Sup,Obs: Terminal outcomes are explicit · resolved · linked · filed · aborted<br/>Scenario eval (test_helpdesk_agent_scenarios.py) asserts<br/>mock-conversation -> expected next_action without AWS / GitHub
